sentences.english: I still heard them even in Asian dens and German gutters.
sentences.chinese: 我仍然聽見了他們甚而在亞洲穴和德國天溝。

sentences.english: If valley flashings are too narrow, backed-up water can find its way under the roofing materials.
sentences.chinese: 如果天溝過於窄的話，積水將滲透屋面材料。

sentences.english: The invention relates to a gutter snow melting plate.
sentences.chinese: 本發明涉及到一種天溝融雪板。
